snippet.title: Aurascope Devlog #1 - A first in-depth look
snippet.description:
This is an indie game my friend Jonah and I have been working on for the last couple months, you could say it's a spiritual successor to PSF in a lot of ways. We're putting so much time and effort into this game to really make it something special. A like and subscribe would go a long way! Thanks so much for watching! Please follow our Twitter and Discord for more updates!
I'll have more about the game to show off on the channel real soon!

Discord:
► https://discord.gg/fcUf8pD

Team Brobro:
► Brobro Studios: https://twitter.com/BrobroStudios
► My Twitter: https://twitter.com/NickOztok
► Jonah's Twitter: https://twitter.com/Jonah_Worley

Special Shoutouts to our Composer Zach for making the amazing music and sound effects!
He deserves a follow, and be sure to check out his soundcloud! 
► https://twitter.com/zstriefel
► https://soundcloud.com/zachstriefel

Also some more shoutouts to our amazing spriters Franek and Neweegee! 
Without them the game wouldn't look as beautiful as it does right now! Please follow them too!
► https://twitter.com/Franrekkk
► https://twitter.com/Neweegee
